text: Stupak is an occupational surname of Ukrainian origin, which means "horse mill", or a worker at a horse-powered mill. The name may refer to: *Alex Stupak (born 1980), American chef *Bart Stupak (born 1952), American politician *Bec Stupak (born 1974), American artist *Bob Stupak (1942–2009), American businessman Category:Ukrainian-language surnames
title: Stupak
